3 for the whole week , please !	the weather next_week for grand_rapids is going to be a series of ups and downs from rain on friday to a clear_skies on thursday and to rain on sunday the highs are forecast to be near 100f with lows near 30f
4 thank you so much for the information	you are welcome have a good day

3 for the whole week , please !	the weather next_week for san_mateo is going to be a series of ups and downs from hot on wednesday to a overcast on thursday and to foggy on friday the highs are forecast to be near 100f with lows near 20f
4 thank you so much for the information	you are welcome have a good day
